data.title: Balwant Singh stats and ratings
data.meta_description: Balwant Singh profile player page. Goals, matches, stats, player ratings and more.
data.text:
Balwant Singh is 37 years old (Dec 15, 1986), 180 cm tall and plays for Delhi FC.

Balwant Singh prefers to play with both feet. His jersey number is 15.

If Balwant Singh is going to be in Delhi FC lineup, it will be confirmed on Sofascore one hour before the match starts.

If Balwant Singh plays you will also be able to follow his live Sofascore rating, statistics and heatmap. Balwant Singh football player profile displays all matches and competitions with statistics for all the matches Balwant Singh played in. Most important stats for each competition, including average Sofascore rating, matches played, goals, assists, cards and other relevant data are also displayed.
